Iterator<Set<C>> getNeighborhoodShellIterator(C cell)
Gets an iterator over cells in the neighborhood of the given cell. The definition of "neighborhood" is implementation-specific, and may have parameters (such as a radius).

Parameters:
cell - the cell whose neighborhood to iterate over.
Returns:
an iterator over cells in the neighborhood, in no particular order.
